metadata.name: Yissy García
metadata.description:
Yissy García is a young Cuban percussionist who has played in several groups and genres.

She represents progress, her bright eyes and her spectacular musical brain open new roads, without any fear.

When I listen to her music, I do not only feel that it is impressive, but also that her impetus transcends the stage.

Yissy is the avant-garde, the future vision, the path to travel through.

Her music surpasses her hands, and takes us to other dimensions.
